   - encapsulation
   - abstraction
   - inheritance
       - is-A (extends keywords)
       - has-A 
   - polymorphism
       - overloading
       - overriding
       
5# class-object relation
   - instance block
   - constructor 
   - instance variable/method

6# array
	- declaration
	- initialization

