   - class/method names       
   - variable name
       - final variable
       
12# Operator and Assingment 
   - increment & decrement operator
       - pre (++a, --a)
       - post (a++, a--)         
   - Arithmetic operator (+, -, *, /, %) 
   - string concatenation (+)      
   - relational operator (<, <=, >, >=)
   - equality operator (!=, ==)
   - instanceof operator
   - bitwise operator (&, |, ^, ~)
   - not operator (!)
   - conditional operator (&&, ||)
   - compound assignment operator (+=, -=, *=, /=, %=, &=, |=, ^=, >>=, >>>=, <<=)
   - conditional operator (?, :)
   - new operator 
   - [] operator
   
13# flow control
   - if-else 
   - switch..case..default
      - allowed type -> byte(Byte), short(Short), char(Character), int(Integer), enum, String
   - while
   - do..while
   - for, for-each
   - break
   - continue 
   - return
   - try..catch..finally 
   - assert              
                   